Entries.default: "You sure you're in the right place?"
"Fart in front of the queen once, and now I'm stuck down here."
"Heard the trading companies are meeting with Onekaza up at Kahanga palace."
"I saw the hazanui storming up the steps to the palace. Wonder what for?"
"The Vailians got their fancy undies in a bunch over something happening at the palace."
"I heard we might've found Ukaizo. You think it's true?"
"Ukaizo... that can't be real, can it? I thought it was a tale for children."
"Something's going on at the palace. The Rauataians have been shouting at the queen all day."
"I heard the trading companies are meeting with the queen today. Something about a destroyed fort?"
